                                    <persName xml:lang="eng">Ḥunayn ibn Isḥāq‏</persName>
                                    <persName xml:lang="ara">حنين بن إسحق</persName>
                                </name>
                            </author>

                            <title>
                                <title xml:lang="eng" type="desc">Galen's Commentary on the
                                    Hippocratic Aphorisms</title>
                                <title xml:lang="ara">شرح فصول أبقراط لجالينوس</title>
                                <title xml:lang="eng" type="alt">Sharḥ Fuṣūl Abuqrāṭ
                                    li-Gālīnūs</title>
                            </title>
                            <note> This is a thematically arranged collection of the Hippocratic
                                lemmata of <persName ref="viaf.org/viaf/19690624"
                                >Ḥunayn</persName>'s version in 12 chapters. The introduction begins
                                on f. 1b and the table of contents is in ff. 1b-3a. The beginning of
                                each chapter is as follows: Ch 1: 3b; Ch 2: 3b; Ch 3: 16a; Ch 4:
                                18a; Ch 5: 21a; Ch 6: 25a; Ch 7: 29a; Ch 8: 31b; Ch 9: 32b; Ch 10:
                                34a; Ch 11: 35b; Ch 12: 38a.</note>
